---
// Support section - "How We Support This"
---

<section class="relative py-32 z-10">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-lituus-pink uppercase mb-4 block">
          Taking The Leap In
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-8">
          Enabling
        <span class="font-serif italic ml-2">The Future</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg font-light text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        To ensure this infrastructure gets built right, we've set aside
        treasury resources for independent teams working on the problem. We
        believe the best path forward comes from parallel innovation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="inline-grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:divide-x divide-white/20 items-center gap-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="px-8">
        <span class="text-3xl font-serif text-white block mb-1">
          Treasury
        </span>
        <span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest text-lituus-pink uppercase">
          Dedicated Resources
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="px-8">
        <span class="text-3xl font-serif text-white block mb-1">
          Independent
        </span>
        <span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest text-lituus-pink uppercase">
          Multiple Teams
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
